## Creating a transparent background

to make an image have a colour as transparent.
1. Load the image into gimp.
2. Use the "fuzzy select tool" to select a region
3. select colours->color to alpha and click ok.
4. select the eraser tool and erase the background colour

## Library Variables
'sdl2-config --static-libs' gives us the library variables.

